{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"How many of you had to fill out a web form"},{"time":2024,"text":"where you've been asked to read"},{"time":3560,"text":"a distorted sequence\nof characters like this?"},{"time":5720,"text":"How many of you found it really annoying?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":7697,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":8820,"text":"OK, outstanding. So I invented that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":10580,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":12440,"text":"Or I was one of the people who did it."},{"time":14320,"text":"That thing is called a CAPTCHA."},{"time":15880,"text":"And it is there to make sure\nyou, the entity filling out the form,"},{"time":19040,"text":"are a human and not a computer program"},{"time":20920,"text":"that was written to submit\nthe form millions of times."},{"time":23520,"text":"The reason it works is because humans,\nat least non-visually-impaired humans,"},{"time":27200,"text":"have no trouble reading\nthese distorted characters,"},{"time":29640,"text":"whereas programs can't do it as well yet."},{"time":31640,"text":"In the case of Ticketmaster,"},{"time":33160,"text":"the reason you have\nto type these characters"},{"time":35280,"text":"is to prevent scalpers\nfrom writing a program"},{"time":37440,"text":"that can buy millions\nof tickets, two at a time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39720,"text":"CAPTCHAs are used all over the Internet."},{"time":41680,"text":"And since they're used so often,"},{"time":43280,"text":"a lot of times the sequence\nof random characters shown to the user"},{"time":46440,"text":"is not so fortunate."},{"time":47680,"text":"So this is an example\nfrom the Yahoo registration page."},{"time":50360,"text":"The random characters\nthat happened to be shown to the user"},{"time":53200,"text":"were W, A, I, T,\nwhich, of course, spell a word."},{"time":55920,"text":"But the best part is the message"},{"time":58040,"text":"that the Yahoo help desk\ngot about 20 minutes later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60520,"text":"[Help! I've been waiting\nfor over 20 minutes and nothing happens.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":63680,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":68560,"text":"This person thought they needed to wait."},{"time":70489,"text":"This, of course,\nis not as bad as this poor person."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":75320,"text":"CAPTCHA Project is something that we did\nat Carnegie Melllon over 10 years ago,"},{"time":79080,"text":"and it's been used everywhere."},{"time":80560,"text":"Let me now tell you about a project\nthat we did a few years later,"},{"time":83720,"text":"which is sort of\nthe next evolution of CAPTCHA."},{"time":85960,"text":"This is a project that we call reCAPTCHA,"},{"time":87960,"text":"which is something that we started\nhere at Carnegie Mellon,"},{"time":90760,"text":"then we turned it into a start-up company."},{"time":92792,"text":"And then about a year and a half ago,\nGoogle actually acquired this company."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96404,"text":"Let me tell you what this project started."},{"time":98435,"text":"This project started\nfrom the following realization:"},{"time":100990,"text":"It turns out that approximately\n200 million CAPTCHAs"},{"time":103451,"text":"are typed everyday\nby people around the world."},{"time":105626,"text":"When I first heard this,\nI was quite proud of myself."},{"time":108134,"text":"I thought, look at the impact\nmy research has had."},{"time":110499,"text":"But then I started feeling bad."},{"time":112007,"text":"Here's the thing:\neach time you type a CAPTCHA,"},{"time":114237,"text":"essentially, you waste\n10 seconds of your time."},{"time":116600,"text":"And if you multiply that by 200 million,"},{"time":118560,"text":"you get that humanity is wasting\nabout 500,000 hours every day"},{"time":121600,"text":"typing these annoying CAPTCHAs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":124200,"text":"So then I started feeling bad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125653,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":127480,"text":"And then I started thinking, of course,\nwe can't just get rid of CAPTCHAs,"},{"time":131000,"text":"because the security of the web\ndepends on them."},{"time":133280,"text":"But then I started thinking,\ncan we use this effort"},{"time":135720,"text":"for something that is good for humanity?"},{"time":137680,"text":"So see, here's the thing."},{"time":139200,"text":"While you're typing a CAPTCHA,\nduring those 10 seconds,"},{"time":141840,"text":"your brain is doing something amazing."},{"time":143720,"text":"Your brain is doing something\nthat computers cannot yet do."},{"time":146560,"text":"So can we get you to do useful work\nfor those 10 seconds?"},{"time":149280,"text":"Is there some humongous problem\nthat we cannot yet get computers to solve,"},{"time":152800,"text":"yet we can split\ninto tiny 10-second chunks"},{"time":155600,"text":"such that each time\nsomebody solves a CAPTCHA,"},{"time":157800,"text":"they solve a little bit of this problem?"},{"time":159760,"text":"And the answer to that is \"yes,\"\nand this is what we're doing now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162920,"text":"Nowadays, while you're typing a CAPTCHA,"},{"time":164880,"text":"not only are you authenticating\nyourself as a human,"},{"time":167333,"text":"but in addition you're helping us\nto digitize books."},{"time":169800,"text":"Let me explain how this works."},{"time":171280,"text":"There's a lot of projects\ntrying to digitize books."},{"time":173720,"text":"Google has one.\nThe Internet Archive has one."},{"time":175880,"text":"Amazon, with the Kindle,\nis trying to digitize books."},{"time":178400,"text":"Basically, the way this works\nis you start with an old book."},{"time":181600,"text":"You've seen those things, right?"},{"time":183200,"text":"Like a book?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":184440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":185720,"text":"So you start with a book\nand then you scan it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188280,"text":"Now, scanning a book"},{"time":189520,"text":"is like taking a digital\nphotograph of every page."},{"time":191920,"text":"It gives you an image for every page."},{"time":193760,"text":"This is an image with text\nfor every page of the book."},{"time":196360,"text":"The next step in the process\nis that the computer needs to be able"},{"time":199520,"text":"to decipher the words in this image."},{"time":201280,"text":"That's using a technology called OCR,\nfor optical character recognition,"},{"time":204720,"text":"which takes a picture of text"},{"time":206160,"text":"and tries to figure out\nwhat text is in there."},{"time":208360,"text":"Now, the problem\nis that OCR is not perfect."},{"time":211040,"text":"Especially for older books"},{"time":212480,"text":"where the ink has faded\nand the pages have turned yellow,"},{"time":215640,"text":"OCR cannot recognize a lot of the words."},{"time":217600,"text":"For things that were written\nmore than 50 years ago,"},{"time":220080,"text":"the computer cannot recognize\nabout 30 percent of the words."},{"time":222960,"text":"So now we're taking all of the words\nthat the computer cannot recognize"},{"time":226360,"text":"and we're getting people\nto read them for us"},{"time":228640,"text":"while they're typing\na CAPTCHA on the Internet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230880,"text":"So the next time you type a CAPTCHA,\nthese words that you're typing"},{"time":234080,"text":"are actually words from books\nthat are being digitized"},{"time":236680,"text":"that the computer could not recognize."},{"time":238560,"text":"The reason we have\ntwo words nowadays instead of one"},{"time":241040,"text":"is because one of the words"},{"time":242480,"text":"is a word that the system\njust got out of a book,"},{"time":245080,"text":"it didn't know what it was\nand it's going to present it to you."},{"time":248120,"text":"But since it doesn't know the answer,\nit cannot grade it."},{"time":250840,"text":"So we give you another word,"},{"time":252240,"text":"for which the system does know the answer."},{"time":254264,"text":"We don't tell you which one's which\nand we say, please type both."},{"time":257360,"text":"And if you type the correct word"},{"time":258959,"text":"for the one for which\nthe system knows the answer,"},{"time":261360,"text":"it assumes you are human"},{"time":262640,"text":"and it also gets some confidence\nthat you typed the other word correctly."},{"time":266120,"text":"And if we repeat this process\nto 10 different people"},{"time":268600,"text":"and they agree on what the new word is,"},{"time":270520,"text":"then we get one more word\ndigitized accurately."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272760,"text":"So this is how the system works."},{"time":274360,"text":"And since we released it\nabout three or four years ago,"},{"time":277000,"text":"a lot of websites have started\nswitching from the old CAPTCHA,"},{"time":279960,"text":"where people wasted their time,"},{"time":281520,"text":"to the new CAPTCHA where people\nare helping to digitize books."},{"time":284480,"text":"So every time you buy\ntickets on Ticketmaster,"},{"time":286680,"text":"you help to digitize a book."},{"time":288080,"text":"Facebook: Every time\nyou add a friend or poke somebody,"},{"time":290720,"text":"you help to digitize a book."},{"time":292120,"text":"Twitter and about 350,000 other sites\nare all using reCAPTCHA."},{"time":295080,"text":"And the number of sites\nthat are using reCAPTCHA is so high"},{"time":297920,"text":"that the number of words\nwe're digitizing per day is really large."},{"time":301080,"text":"It's about 100 million a day,"},{"time":302520,"text":"which is the equivalent of about\ntwo and a half million books a year."},{"time":306040,"text":"And this is all being done\none word at a time"},{"time":308200,"text":"by just people typing\nCAPTCHAs on the Internet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310440,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":317680,"text":"Now, of course,"},{"time":318920,"text":"since we're doing so many words per day,"},{"time":322280,"text":"funny things can happen."},{"time":323560,"text":"This is especially true\nbecause now we're giving people"},{"time":326200,"text":"two randomly chosen English words\nnext to each other."},{"time":328720,"text":"So funny things can happen."},{"time":330080,"text":"For example, we presented this word."},{"time":331840,"text":"It's the word \"Christians\";\nthere's nothing wrong with it."},{"time":334600,"text":"But if you present it along\nwith another randomly chosen word,"},{"time":337560,"text":"bad things can happen."},{"time":338920,"text":"So we get this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340160,"text":"[bad Christians]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":341400,"text":"But it's even worse, because\nthe website where we showed this"},{"time":344320,"text":"actually happened to be called\nThe Embassy of the Kingdom of God."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":349120,"text":"Oops."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350360,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":354240,"text":"Here's another really bad one."},{"time":355960,"text":"JohnEdwards.com"}]},{"cues":[{"time":357280,"text":"[Damn liberal]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":358520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":363040,"text":"So we keep on insulting people\nleft and right everyday."},{"time":365880,"text":"Of course, we're not\njust insulting people."},{"time":367920,"text":"Here's the thing. Since we're presenting\ntwo randomly chosen words,"},{"time":371120,"text":"interesting things can happen."},{"time":372600,"text":"So this actually has given rise\nto a really big Internet meme"},{"time":377240,"text":"that tens of thousands of people\nhave participated in,"},{"time":379800,"text":"which is called CAPTCHA art."},{"time":381480,"text":"I'm sure some of you have heard about it."},{"time":383480,"text":"Here's how it works."},{"time":384760,"text":"Imagine you're using the Internet\nand you see a CAPTCHA"},{"time":387400,"text":"that you think is somewhat peculiar,"},{"time":389160,"text":"like this CAPTCHA."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390400,"text":"[invisible toaster]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":391640,"text":"What you're supposed to do\nis you take a screenshot of it."},{"time":394400,"text":"Then of course, you fill out the CAPTCHA\nbecause you help us digitize a book."},{"time":398080,"text":"But first you take a screenshot"},{"time":399600,"text":"and then you draw something\nthat is related to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":402000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":403720,"text":"That's how it works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404960,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406320,"text":"There are tens of thousands of these."},{"time":409000,"text":"Some of them are very cute."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411096,"text":"[clenched it]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":412333,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":414200,"text":"Some of them are funnier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":415760,"text":"[stoned Founders]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":417000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":421400,"text":"And some of them,\nlike paleontological shvisle ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424853,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":426800,"text":"they contain Snoop Dogg."}]},{"cues":[{"time":428040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":431200,"text":"OK, so this is my favorite\nnumber of reCAPTCHA."},{"time":433800,"text":"So this is the favorite thing\nthat I like about this whole project."},{"time":437000,"text":"This is the number of distinct people"},{"time":438840,"text":"that have helped us digitize at least\none word out of a book through reCAPTCHA:"},{"time":442600,"text":"750 million, a little over 10 percent\nof the world's population,"},{"time":445680,"text":"has helped us digitize human knowledge."},{"time":447600,"text":"And it is numbers like these\nthat motivate my research agenda."},{"time":450720,"text":"So the question that motivates\nmy research is the following:"},{"time":453800,"text":"If you look at humanity's\nlarge-scale achievements,"},{"time":456240,"text":"these really big things"},{"time":457480,"text":"that humanity has gotten together\nand done historically --"},{"time":460219,"text":"like, for example,\nbuilding the pyramids of Egypt"},{"time":462720,"text":"or the Panama Canal"},{"time":464320,"text":"or putting a man on the Moon --"},{"time":466400,"text":"there is a curious fact about them,"},{"time":468120,"text":"and it is that they were all done\nwith about the same number of people."},{"time":471480,"text":"It's weird; they were all done\nwith about 100,000 people."},{"time":474200,"text":"And the reason for that is because,\nbefore the Internet,"},{"time":476880,"text":"coordinating more than 100,000 people,"},{"time":478760,"text":"let alone paying them,\nwas essentially impossible."},{"time":481800,"text":"But now with the Internet,\nI've just shown you a project"},{"time":484480,"text":"where we've gotten 750 million people\nto help us digitize human knowledge."},{"time":488000,"text":"So the question\nthat motivates my research is,"},{"time":490200,"text":"if we can put a man\non the Moon with 100,000,"},{"time":492360,"text":"what can we do with 100 million?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":494560,"text":"So based on this question,"},{"time":495840,"text":"we've had a lot of different projects\nthat we've been working on."},{"time":498920,"text":"Let me tell you about one\nthat I'm most excited about."},{"time":501480,"text":"This is something that we've been\nsemiquietly working on"},{"time":504160,"text":"for the last year and a half or so."},{"time":505880,"text":"It hasn't yet been launched.\nIt's called Duolingo."},{"time":508280,"text":"Since it hasn't been launched, shhh!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":510040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":511720,"text":"Yeah, I can trust you'll do that."},{"time":514000,"text":"So this is the project.\nHere's how it started."},{"time":516240,"text":"It started with me posing a question\nto my graduate student, Severin Hacker."},{"time":519840,"text":"OK, that's Severin Hacker."},{"time":522039,"text":"So I posed the question\nto my graduate student."},{"time":524280,"text":"By the way, you did hear me correctly;\nhis last name is Hacker."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":528320,"text":"So I posed this question to him:\nHow can we get 100 million people"},{"time":531640,"text":"translating the web\ninto every major language for free?"},{"time":535240,"text":"There's a lot of things\nto say about this question."},{"time":537680,"text":"First of all, translating the web."},{"time":539360,"text":"Right now, the web\nis partitioned into multiple languages."},{"time":542180,"text":"A large fraction of it is in English."},{"time":544020,"text":"If you don't know English,\nyou can't access it."},{"time":546260,"text":"But there's large fractions\nin other different languages,"},{"time":548980,"text":"and if you don't know them,\nyou can't access it."},{"time":551260,"text":"So I would like to translate\nall of the web,"},{"time":553380,"text":"or at least most of it,\ninto every major language."},{"time":555780,"text":"That's what I would like to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557300,"text":"Now, some of you may say,\nwhy can't we use computers to translate?"},{"time":561800,"text":"Machine translation\nis starting to translate"},{"time":563920,"text":"some sentences here and there."},{"time":565400,"text":"Why can't we use it to translate the web?"},{"time":567400,"text":"The problem with that\nis it's not yet good enough"},{"time":569760,"text":"and it probably won't be\nfor the next 15 to 20 years."},{"time":572280,"text":"It makes a lot of mistakes.\nEven when it doesn't,"},{"time":574640,"text":"since it makes so many mistakes,\nyou don't know whether to trust it or not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":578240,"text":"So let me show you an example"},{"time":579680,"text":"of something that was\ntranslated with a machine."},{"time":581960,"text":"Actually, it was a forum post."},{"time":583440,"text":"It was somebody who was trying\nto ask a question about JavaScript."},{"time":586640,"text":"It was translated\nfrom Japanese into English."},{"time":589280,"text":"So I'll just let you read."},{"time":591080,"text":"This person starts apologizing"},{"time":592880,"text":"for the fact that\nit's translated with a computer."},{"time":595360,"text":"So the next sentence is going to be\nthe preamble to the question."},{"time":599160,"text":"So he's just explaining something."},{"time":600840,"text":"Remember, it's a question\nabout JavaScript."}]},{"cues":[{"time":602920,"text":"[At often, the goat-time\ninstall a error is vomit.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":605560,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":610680,"text":"Then comes the first part of the question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":614240,"text":"[How many times like the wind,\na pole, and the dragon?]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":617200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":621880,"text":"Then comes my favorite part\nof the question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":623960,"text":"[This insult to father's stones?]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":625920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":629800,"text":"And then comes the ending,"},{"time":631120,"text":"which is my favorite part\nof the whole thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":633280,"text":"[Please apologize for your stupidity.\nThere are a many thank you.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":636440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":638640,"text":"OK, so computer translation,\nnot yet good enough."},{"time":641600,"text":"So back to the question."},{"time":642880,"text":"So we need people\nto translate the whole web."},{"time":645880,"text":"So now the next question you may have is,"},{"time":647880,"text":"well, why can't we just\npay people to do this?"},{"time":650080,"text":"We could pay professional translators\nto translate the whole web."},{"time":653200,"text":"We could do that."},{"time":654480,"text":"Unfortunately, it would be\nextremely expensive."},{"time":656720,"text":"For example, translating a tiny fraction\nof the whole web, Wikipedia,"},{"time":660000,"text":"into one other language, Spanish."},{"time":662520,"text":"OK? Wikipedia exists in Spanish,"},{"time":664520,"text":"but it's very small\ncompared to the size of English."},{"time":667000,"text":"It's about 20 percent\nof the size of English."},{"time":669200,"text":"If we wanted to translate\nthe other 80 percent into Spanish,"},{"time":672080,"text":"it would cost at least\n50 million dollars --"},{"time":674240,"text":"and this is even at the most exploited,\noutsourcing country out there."},{"time":677920,"text":"So it would be very expensive."},{"time":679400,"text":"So what we want to do is,\nwe want to get 100 million people"},{"time":682186,"text":"translating the web\ninto every major language for free."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684800,"text":"If this is what you want to do,\nyou quickly realize"},{"time":687240,"text":"you're going to run\ninto two big hurdles, two big obstacles."},{"time":690200,"text":"The first one is a lack of bilinguals."},{"time":693520,"text":"So I don't even know"},{"time":695720,"text":"if there exists 100 million people\nout there using the web"},{"time":698480,"text":"who are bilingual enough\nto help us translate."},{"time":700800,"text":"That's a big problem."},{"time":702040,"text":"The other problem you're going to run into\nis a lack of motivation."},{"time":705240,"text":"How are we going to motivate people\nto actually translate the web for free?"},{"time":708800,"text":"Normally, you have to pay\npeople to do this."},{"time":711120,"text":"So how are we going to motivate them\nto do it for free?"},{"time":713760,"text":"When we were starting to think about this,\nwe were blocked by these two things."},{"time":717520,"text":"But then we realized, there's a way"},{"time":719240,"text":"to solve both these problems\nwith the same solution."},{"time":721720,"text":"To kill two birds with one stone."},{"time":723360,"text":"And that is to transform\nlanguage translation"},{"time":725520,"text":"into something that millions\nof people want to do"},{"time":728360,"text":"and that also helps\nwith the problem of lack of bilinguals,"},{"time":731520,"text":"and that is language education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":733920,"text":"So it turns out that today,"},{"time":735920,"text":"there are over 1.2 billion people\nlearning a foreign language."},{"time":740040,"text":"People really want\nto learn a foreign language."},{"time":742280,"text":"And it's not just because\nthey're being forced to do so in school."},{"time":745440,"text":"In the US alone,\nthere are over five million people"},{"time":747880,"text":"who have paid over $500\nfor software to learn a new language."},{"time":750800,"text":"So people really want\nto learn a new language."},{"time":753000,"text":"So what we've been working on\nfor the last year and a half"},{"time":755760,"text":"is a new website --\nit's called Duolingo --"},{"time":757840,"text":"where the basic idea is\npeople learn a new language for free"},{"time":760720,"text":"while simultaneously translating the web."},{"time":762800,"text":"And so basically,\nthey're learning by doing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":765360,"text":"So the way this works"},{"time":766600,"text":"is whenever you're a just a beginner,\nwe give you very simple sentences."},{"time":770040,"text":"There's a lot of very simple\nsentences on the web."},{"time":772440,"text":"We give you very simple sentences\nalong with what each word means."},{"time":775680,"text":"And as you translate them"},{"time":777040,"text":"and as you see how other people\ntranslate them,"},{"time":779280,"text":"you start learning the language."},{"time":780880,"text":"And as you get more advanced,"},{"time":782320,"text":"we give you more complex\nsentences to translate."},{"time":784600,"text":"But at all times,\nyou're learning by doing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":786640,"text":"Now, the crazy thing about this method\nis that it actually really works."},{"time":790360,"text":"People are really learning a language."},{"time":792240,"text":"We're mostly done building it\nand now we're testing it."},{"time":794880,"text":"People really can\nlearn a language with it."},{"time":796960,"text":"And they learn it about as well\nas the leading language learning software."},{"time":800480,"text":"So people really do learn a language."},{"time":802320,"text":"And not only do they learn it as well,\nbut actually it's more interesting."},{"time":805840,"text":"Because with Duolingo,\npeople are learning with real content."},{"time":808760,"text":"As opposed to learning\nwith made-up sentences,"},{"time":810960,"text":"people are learning with real content,\nwhich is inherently interesting."},{"time":814320,"text":"So people really do learn a language."}]},{"cues":[{"time":816160,"text":"But perhaps more surprisingly,"},{"time":817800,"text":"the translations that we get\nfrom people using the site,"},{"time":820560,"text":"even though they're just beginners,"},{"time":822360,"text":"the translations that we get"},{"time":823760,"text":"are as accurate as those\nof professional language translators,"},{"time":826720,"text":"which is very surprising."},{"time":827960,"text":"So let me show you one example."},{"time":829520,"text":"This is a sentence that was translated\nfrom German into English."},{"time":832560,"text":"The top is the German.\nThe middle is an English translation"},{"time":835360,"text":"that was done by a professional translator"},{"time":837640,"text":"who we paid 20 cents a word\nfor this translation."},{"time":840040,"text":"And the bottom is a translation\nby users of Duolingo,"},{"time":842760,"text":"none of whom knew any German\nbefore they started using the site."},{"time":846520,"text":"If you can see, it's pretty much perfect."},{"time":848520,"text":"Of course, we play a trick here"},{"time":850080,"text":"to make the translations as good\nas professional language translators."},{"time":853440,"text":"We combine the translations\nof multiple beginners"},{"time":855800,"text":"to get the quality\nof a single professional translator."}]},{"cues":[{"time":858720,"text":"Now, even though\nwe're combining the translations,"},{"time":863280,"text":"the site actually\ncan translate pretty fast."},{"time":866080,"text":"So let me show you,"},{"time":867320,"text":"this is our estimates\nof how fast we could translate Wikipedia"},{"time":870280,"text":"from English into Spanish."},{"time":871600,"text":"Remember, this is\n50 million dollars' worth of value."},{"time":874600,"text":"So if we wanted to translate\nWikipedia into Spanish,"},{"time":877080,"text":"we could do it in five weeks\nwith 100,000 active users."},{"time":879800,"text":"And we could do it in about 80 hours\nwith a million active users."},{"time":882880,"text":"Since all the projects\nmy group has worked on so far"},{"time":885360,"text":"have gotten millions of users,"},{"time":886840,"text":"we're hopeful that we'll be able\nto translate extremely fast."}]},{"cues":[{"time":889760,"text":"Now, the thing that\nI'm most excited about with Duolingo"},{"time":892760,"text":"is I think this provides a fair\nbusiness model for language education."},{"time":896520,"text":"So here's the thing:"},{"time":897760,"text":"The current business model\nfor language education"},{"time":900120,"text":"is the student pays,"},{"time":901520,"text":"and in particular, the student\npays Rosetta Stone 500 dollars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":904600,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":906440,"text":"That's the current business model."},{"time":908120,"text":"The problem with this business model"},{"time":909880,"text":"is that 95 percent of the world's\npopulation doesn't have 500 dollars."},{"time":913200,"text":"So it's extremely unfair towards the poor."},{"time":916000,"text":"This is totally biased towards the rich."},{"time":917960,"text":"Now, see, in Duolingo,"},{"time":919600,"text":"because while you learn,\nyou're actually creating value,"},{"time":923280,"text":"you're translating stuff --"},{"time":924640,"text":"which, for example, we could\ncharge somebody for translations,"},{"time":927600,"text":"so this is how we could monetize this."},{"time":929480,"text":"Since people are creating value\nwhile they're learning,"},{"time":932120,"text":"they don't have to pay with their money,\nthey pay with their time."},{"time":935240,"text":"But the magical thing here"},{"time":937187,"text":"is that is time that would have had\nto have been spent anyways"},{"time":940207,"text":"learning the language."},{"time":941440,"text":"So the nice thing about Duolingo"},{"time":943040,"text":"is, I think, it provides\na fair business model --"},{"time":945400,"text":"one that doesn't discriminate\nagainst poor people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":947800,"text":"So here's the site. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":949280,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":957800,"text":"We haven't yet launched,"},{"time":960240,"text":"but if you go there, you can sign up\nto be part of our private beta,"},{"time":963560,"text":"which is probably going to start\nin three or four weeks."},{"time":966240,"text":"We haven't yet launched it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":967600,"text":"By the way, I'm the one talking here,"},{"time":969440,"text":"but Duolingo is the work\nof a really awesome team,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":971840,"text":"some of whom are here. So thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":973600,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}